{"tid":924273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗16歲仔留書墮樓　頭部重創送院搶救","createTime":"2018-12-02T03:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T06:15:27.000Z","uid":160807,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a211ac37e0a7a96ea05cd95203d4fba8a7c1e7","tid":924273,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181201/_2018120207593041377.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181201%2F_2018120207593041377.jpg&h=10969214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名16歲少年昨晚9時許由深水埗元州街1號高處墮下，重傷倒卧路邊。他事後由救護車送院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚9時12分接獲男途人報案，指聽到一聲巨響，發現少年倒卧上址，懷疑從高處墮下。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，少年頭部重創，昏迷送瑪嘉烈醫院治理。警方於現場發現遺書，初步調查相信從上址一單位墮下，事件沒有可疑。少年搶救期間，一名女親友趕抵醫院等候消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1378002/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1378002%2F&d=siact7mot2Oi48hSsu2n1bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=36ece410\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1378002%2F&h=12b439f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1378002/</a>"},{"pid":"1158fce8c56028dd747ff93693af7d1ee2775a2b","tid":924273,"uid":118647,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:33:15.000Z","msg":"死唔去手尾長，搵高啲先跳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07986670835e0c0e364c873c3c5182e2b3294232","tid":924273,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:38:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">深水埗</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3b66ba5acf93e534182d84438acef751044978dd","tid":924273,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img